  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You put your all into a single shot with your ranged weapon, intended to end the fight with prejudice intent. Make a ranged Taijutsu attack, dealing your [weapons damage] + 6d8 and forcing the target creature to make a Constitution saving throw, being staggered on a failed save.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast as a Chain 2, increase the damage die by +4, if this jutsu is cast as a Chain 3, increase the damage die by an additional +2.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above A-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d8</p>",
